column5: And to add to this for those Turkey hunters. The season is NOT open on the 25 of April.It opens the 27th,yes a Monday. Thanks Wayne for the info.
the vet just told my wife our cats in season if anyone is interested in shooting it
I guess they don't think anyone hunts north of Sudbury.  Pam
I don't know why they bother, they're going to do whatever they want regardless of the input. They probably already have the changes drawn up and this is a formality.
Season started early for ya up in Simcoe eh?  The old man's ran away for a few days and got prego in the process, that was back in December...  Something on your mind Terry?!
